  "description": "<i>Tetrix</i> is an advanced and highly polished kind of <i><a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Tetris\">Tetris</a></i> for the Amiga. There are four game modes: 1P solo, 2P duet, 2P duel and tournament. In the solo and duet modes, the game doesn't just play until you lose by filling the screen. Instead, you are given challenges to complete, preferably within a given time. This may involve removing a set number of lines, removing pieces placed on the screen beforehand, surviving 50 drops, playing with reverse controls, and so on.",
